Package: R2scGEO
Title: Query and Load Public scRNA-seq Datasets from GEO
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ryan", "Reis", email = "ryanreis333@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight toolkit to search NCBI GEO for single-cell RNA-seq
    series, inspect their metadata, list and download supplementary files,
    and load 10x-style sparse matrices into Seurat or SingleCellExperiment
    objects. Downloads are cached on disk to avoid repeated queries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
